s:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8G0","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33693,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/09\/fadl-abu-bakr-umar-ammar\/","url_meta":{"origin":33356,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Virtues of Abu Bakr, Umar, \u2018Ammar, and Ibn Mas\u2019ud","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFollow these two men from my companions after me, Abu Bakr and Umar. Accept the guidance of \u2018Ammar, and take the advice of Ibn Mas\u2019ud.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3805 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11077,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/after-prophet-khulafah-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":33356,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: After the Prophet, follow Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: We were sitting with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cI surely do not know how much longer I will remain with you. After me, follow these two,\u201d and the Prophet pointed to Abu Bakr and Umar. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3663 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/04\/04\/four-khulafa-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":33356,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet foretells Four Righteous Caliphs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Safinah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Caliphate after me will last for thirty years, then there will be kingship.\u201d Sa\u2019id said to Safinah, \u201cCount the Caliphates of Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman?\u201d Then, Safinah said, \u201cYou must count the Caliphate of Ali.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":33356,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43677,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/abu-bakr-umar-honored-ummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33356,"posit